{"type":"answer","id":4007,"parentType":"question","parentId":1016,"uid":915,"contents":"具体人数已不可考证，大约四千左右，但绝对没有某些媒体宣扬的有上万人，更不可能是政府说的一个人都没死。绝大多数人都是被军队枪杀的，死亡主体是学生，普通市民，还有部分军人。不过坦克事件是有详细说法的，死了五个学生，伤了七个，所有人都有具体的个人信息，现场惨不忍睹，造成了极大的恶劣影响。现场照片如下，不能接受的自觉跳过。<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180524/567651b14628de992f39720970d11623.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180524/567651b14628de992f39720970d11623.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180524/567651b14628de992f39720970d11623.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180524/3c64f140a686b305b21f726c57689230.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180524/3c64f140a686b305b21f726c57689230.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180524/3c64f140a686b305b21f726c57689230.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180524/a4a719fd8ef240a46568716f097e6a9f.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180524/a4a719fd8ef240a46568716f097e6a9f.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180524/a4a719fd8ef240a46568716f097e6a9f.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180524/90b6504b9020a3959db00e2fa05e6a07.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180524/90b6504b9020a3959db00e2fa05e6a07.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180524/90b6504b9020a3959db00e2fa05e6a07.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2018-05-25","agreeCount":5,"discussionCount":0}